      <h2>Our Story & Values</h2>
      
      <div class="content-row">
        <div class="text-content">
          <p>Founded in 2010, Pacific Trails Resort was born out of a passion for the rugged beauty of the North Coast. Our goal is to provide a serene escape where guests can reconnect with nature without sacrificing luxury. Whether you are here for the world-class hiking or a quiet yoga retreat, our team is dedicated to your peace of mind.</p>
          <p>We believe in sustainable tourism and preserving the Big Sur ecosystem for generations to come. Join our family and experience the magic of the Pacific.</p>
